data.description: Welcome to River Place, a quiet, gated community tucked away behind desirable Tara Preserve. This stately 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home has incredible curb appeal with its paver entry, lush landscaping and outdoor lighting. Once inside, you will be taken in by the soaring ceilings and 2 story fireplace that is the focal point of this home. This great room floor plan features tile flooring, a baker's kitchen with solid surface counters, solid wood cabinets, new stainless appliances, including a gas range, separate dining room with bay window, and dinette with slider to lanai. First floor master suite has 2 walk in closets and luxurious master bath. The dramatic stairway leads to 3 additional bedrooms and a spacious bath. Recent updates include fresh paint throughout, new stainless steel appliances, and new high end carpet on second floor. Vacation at home in the wonderful pool area with solar heat, LED lighting, and paver pool deck. River Place is a short distance to Lakewood Ranch amenities, dining, shopping, and medical care, and excellent schools. Close proximity to I-75 makes for a short ride to Sarasota or St.Pete/Tampa. The community features large lakefront pool, clubhouse, fitness center, nature trails, and a kayak launch on the Braden River for fishing and exploring nature.  Low HOA fees and No CDD fees!  This home is truly move in ready!
